snippet.title: The Price of Freedom - Official Trailer (2017) - Presented by Construct Studio
snippet.description:
The Price of Freedom - Steam link: http://store.steampowered.com/app/561080/
The Price of Freedom - Viveport link: https://www.viveport.com/apps/ecab36ad-e9cb-4fa3-80ac-4e57579e665e
You are Agent Zero. Your mission: assassinate Benjamin Miller, a radical who broke into CIA facilities and stole top secret chemical weapons research. Your mission quickly takes a dark turn as you learn the truth of what Miller was searching for that night.
